params.nakedBannyId: The ID of the naked banny shows with the associated assets.

returns.outfitIds: The outfits attached to the Naked Banny.
returns.worldId: The world attached to the Naked Banny.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to show. If the ID belongs to a Naked Banny, it will be shown with its current outfits in its current world.

params.owner: The owner allowed to add SVG files that correspond to tier IDs.
params.trustedForwarder: The trusted forwarder for the ERC2771Context.

decorateBannyWith(address,uint256,uint25.details: The caller must own the naked banny being dressed and all outfits being worn.

params.nakedBannyId: The ID of the Naked Banny being dressed.
params.outfitIds: The IDs of the outfits that'll be associated with the specified banny. Only one outfit per outfit category allowed at a time and they must be passed in order.
params.worldId: The ID of the world that'll be associated with the specified banny.

isTrustedForwarder(address).details: Indicates whether any particular address is the trusted forwarder.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params.svgContents: The svg contents being stored, not including the parent <svg></svg> element.
params.tierId: The ID of the tier having an SVG stored.

setSvgHashOf(uint256,bytes32).details: This allows anyone to lazily upload the correct svg file.

params.svgHash: The svg hash being stored, not including the parent <svg></svg> element.
params.tierId: The ID of the tier having an SVG hash stored.

params.name: The name of the tier.
params.tierId: The ID of the tier having its name stored.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to show. If the ID belongs to a Naked Banny, it will be shown with its current outfits in its current world.

returns._0: tokenUri The URI representing the SVG.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

trustedForwarder().details: Returns the address of the trusted forwarder.

assetIdsOf(uint256).notice: The assets currently attached to each Naked Banny, owned by the naked Banny's owner.

bannySvgOf(address,uint256,bool,bool).notice: Returns the SVG showing a dressed Naked Banny.

decorateBannyWith(address,uint256,uint25.notice: Dress your Naked Banny with outfits.

setSvgBaseUriOf(string).notice: Allows the owner of this contract to specify the base of the domain hosting the SVG files.

setSvgContentsOf(uint256,string).notice: The owner of this contract can store SVG files for tier IDs.

setSvgHashOf(uint256,bytes32).notice: Allows the owner of this contract to upload the hash of an svg file for a tierId.

setTierName(uint256,string).notice: Allows the owner to set the tier's name.

svgBaseUri().notice: The base of the domain hosting the SVG files that can be lazily uploaded to the contract.

svgHashOf(uint256).notice: The Naked Banny and outfit SVG hash files.

tokenUriOf(address,uint256).notice: Returns the SVG showing a dressed Naked Banny in a world.
